<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1324507-in-chapter-5-in-my-ebook-version-of-this">In chapter 5 in my ebook version of this book, there are two mentions of someone called &quot;Hider&quot; where it obviously means Hitler. Eg &quot;Two weeks later the Gettysburg Address came back from Hider&quot;. Not sure what page number, as it varies with the font size I select.

Is this mistake there in the printed versions? I suspect it&#39;s an OCR error.</a>
</div>
